(function(skuid){
 var $ = skuid.$;
 $(document.body).one('pageload',function(){
 	var eventDetailModel = skuid.model.getModel('EventDetail');
    var eventDetail = eventDetailModel.getFirstRow();
    var eventPaymentSchedule = eventDetail.Payment_Schedule__c;
    var cutOffDate =  eventDetail.X50_Cutoff_Date__c;
    var cutOffDate1 = eventDetail.Cutoff_Date_1__c;
    var cutOffDate2 = eventDetail.Cutoff_Date_2__c;
    var cutOffDate3 = eventDetail.CutoffDate_3__c;
    console.log(eventPaymentSchedule);
    
    var eventPaymentSchedule2 = eventPaymentSchedule.split('-');
    console.log('----'+eventPaymentSchedule2.length);
    var p1;
    var p2;
    var p3;
    var p4;
   for(var i=0;i<eventPaymentSchedule2.length;++i)
   {
       console.log(i+' : '+eventPaymentSchedule2[i]);
       if(i==0){
           p1 =eventPaymentSchedule2[i];
       }
       if(i==1){
           p2 =eventPaymentSchedule2[i];
       }
       if(i==2){
           p3 =eventPaymentSchedule2[i];
       }
       if(i==3){
           p4 =eventPaymentSchedule2[i];
       }
    }
    console.log(p1);
    console.log(p2);
    console.log(p3);
    var modelA = skuid.model.getModel('EventDetailTemp');
    var a= modelA.createRow({ 
                    additionalConditions: [
                        { field: 'CutoffDate', value: cutOffDate},
                        { field: 'CutoffDate1', value: cutOffDate1},
                        { field: 'CutoffDate2', value: cutOffDate2},
                        { field: 'CutoffDate3', value: cutOffDate3},
                        { field: 'PaymentSchedule1', value: p1},
                        { field: 'PaymentSchedule2', value: p2},
                        { field: 'PaymentSchedule3', value: p3},
                        { field: 'PaymentSchedule4', value: p4},
                    ],doAppend: true});
                    
    modelA.save();
 });
})(skuid);

function check(varCheck)
{
    varCheck.value=varCheck.checked;
    alert('check'+varCheck.checked);
}
(function(skuid){
	var $ = skuid.$;
	$(document.body).one('pageload',function(){
		var ProfileOption = skuid.model.getModel('ProfileOptionVisibility');
        var ProfileOptionVisibility = ProfileOption.getRows();
		
		
		var values ='<table class="table">';
		//Start table Header
		values =values+'<thead>';
		values =values+'<tr>';
		values =values+'<th>Visible</th>';
		values =values+'<th class="text-left">Profile Option</th>';
		values =values+'<th class="normal-font">Default</th>';
	//	values =values+'<th><span class="normal-font">Upgrade Item 1</span><br><span class="big-font">Silver Package</span><i class="fa fa-trash-o" aria-hidden="true"></i></th>';

	//	values =values+'<th><div class="btn-add-item">&#43; Add New Upgrade Item</div></th>';
		values =values+'</tr>';
		values =values+'</thead>';
		//End table Header
		//Start table Body....
		values =values+'<tbody>';
		$.each(ProfileOptionVisibility, function( index, value ) {
			console.log('value.boothStatus'+value.Profile_Option__r.Name);
			values =values+'<tr>';
			if(value.Visible__c){
				values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" value="'+value.Visible__c+'" checked="true" onClick="check(this);"/></td>';
			}
			else{
				values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" value="'+value.Visible__c+'" onClick="check(this); /></td>';
			}
			values =values+'<td class="text-left">'+value.Profile_Option__r.Name+'</td>';
			if(value.Profile_Option__r.Name =='Product Categories' || value.Profile_Option__r.Name =='Product Listing' || value.Profile_Option__r.Name =='Videos' || value.Profile_Option__r.Name =='Show Specials'){
				values =values+'<td><div ><input class="input-text" type="text" value="'+value.Default_Value__c+'" /></div></td>';
			}
			else{
				if(value.Default_Checkbox__c){
					values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" value="'+value.Default_Checkbox__c+'" checked="true" onClick="check(this);" /></td>';
				}
				else{
					values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" value="'+value.Default_Checkbox__c+'" checked="true" onClick="check(this);" /></td>';
				}
			}
			
			//values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" checked /></td>';
			//values =values+'<td><input type="checkbox" checked /></td>';
			values =values+'<td>&nbsp;</td>';
			values =values+'</tr>';
		});

		values =values+'</tbody>';
		//End table Body....
		values =values+'</table>';
		
		$('#sk-tznvM-737').append(values);
	});
	
    

    
})(skuid);
